I figured out how to accomplish this. In main.js I either call ```mainWindow.webContents.reload()``` which does the trick, or I use ```mainWindow.webContents.send( 'ping','wohoo' )``` and add the following to render.js
```
require('electron').ipcRenderer.on('ping', function(event, message) {
    console.log(message);  // Prints "whoooooooh!"
});
```
